{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-032__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-001", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-032", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-032__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "老子 32.1", "sort_key": "032.001", "text_original": "道常無名，樸雖小，天下莫能臣也。", "text_normalized": "道常無名，樸雖小，天下莫能臣也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-032__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-002", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-032", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-032__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "老子 32.2", "sort_key": "032.002", "text_original": "侯王若能守之，萬物將自賓。", "text_normalized": "侯王若能守之，萬物將自賓。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-032__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-003", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-032", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-032__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "老子 32.3", "sort_key": "032.003", "text_original": "天地相合，以降甘露，民莫之令而自均。", "text_normalized": "天地相合，以降甘露，民莫之令而自均。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-032__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-004", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-032", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-032__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "老子 32.4", "sort_key": "032.004", "text_original": "始制有名，名亦既有，夫亦將知止，知止所以不殆。", "text_normalized": "始制有名，名亦既有，夫亦將知止，知止所以不殆。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-032__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-005", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-032", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-032__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "老子 32.5", "sort_key": "032.005", "text_original": "譬道之在天下，猶川谷之於江海。", "text_normalized": "譬道之在天下，猶川谷之於江海。", "notes": ""}
